				<div id="post-1403" class="post-1403 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
                
                		<h3 class="entry-title">Symposia Notice</h3>
                        <span class="small">Posted Sep.2.2015</span>

						<h2>Members:</h2>
<h2>After extensive analysis of the economic conditions and state of our Industry, the Ontario Prospectors Association&#39;s Board of Directors have decided to not proceed with the Sudbury Ontario Exploration &amp; Geoscience Symposium in November.</h2>
<h2>The Spring event&nbsp;(NW Symposium&nbsp;- Thunder Bay, April 5 &amp; 6, 2016 will continue as planned.</h2>
<h2>The Board of Directors regret any inconvenience this decision has caused it&#39;s members and supporters.</h2>
												                </div>
                


